{"tid":1185281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<突發>連登上咗民進黨黨報","createTime":"2019-06-04T07:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T01:29:10.000Z","uid":144372,"like":559,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee2b182d740cbed50d96235f8ba634fa552124d","tid":1185281,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2811324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2811324&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cgkx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b18eb0b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2811324&h=0f47f22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2811324</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜上週六在凱道造勢，狂打經濟牌，轟蔡英文台無法讓百姓安居樂業，說道「新加坡補助青年住宅高達百分之八十，香港有五十，台灣只有百分之零點五，年輕人怎麼辦...」，該話傳入香港的討論區裡，遭香港網友大酸：「條友活係平行時空？」。<br />\n<br />\n香港是出了名的寸土寸金，而韓國瑜的補助五十，被香港網友懷疑是把有50%人住公屋，偷換成補助50%，不過，根據香港媒體報導，在2018年，有8萬港民搶租1千戶公屋，難度之高，讓港民酸說，有人可能排到死也排不到。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜講香港補助的一段話，引發香港網友冷嘲熱諷，香港「連登論壇」上，狂轟韓國瑜「草包」，「條友活係平行時空？」、「嘩我地活係異世界呀」、「保你老母呀」、「入中聯辦取得流料?」、「韓國瑜：『一國兩制運作良好』」、「台灣班低智新物 講咩都會信」、「支國青年50% 香港青年-50%」<br />\n<br />\nPTT網友都笑稱：「韓國瑜被香港網友酸爆，比PTT還酸」、「國際認證草包王」、「香港認證智障wwww」、「光看香港移民台灣的人數逐漸增加，就能知道現實了...」。"},{"pid":"2679599d1fcd70c23c360a4dce4fd3e5da57b6cb","tid":1185281,"uid":144372,"like":410,"dislike":6,"score":404,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpthQlS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpthQlS2.jpg&h=d3f11e4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46aab7b031af46a48c1f91539a2feb6cbbbb3e44","tid":1185281,"uid":31637,"like":731,"dislike":2,"score":729,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"屌, 估唔到連民進黨都有線眼係連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74eb1d222ed8901a28669b8ac7262e24ea7be947","tid":1185281,"uid":392,"like":377,"dislike":1,"score":376,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"呢條友好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14450604643f42992797bf1d0b297dca4a3900e6","tid":1185281,"uid":64073,"like":692,"dislike":3,"score":689,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"台灣記者用ad block 扑晒連仔廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0a94ced85076655173ee0f9eada87e4d459751","tid":1185281,"uid":69753,"like":414,"dislike":3,"score":411,"quote":{"pid":"14450604643f42992797bf1d0b297dca4a3900e6","tid":1185281,"uid":64073,"like":692,"dislike":3,"score":689,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"台灣記者用ad block 扑晒連仔廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲有人唔用adblock?"},{"pid":"28621037c2e32967b30a4a32df21ff68331c1aad","tid":1185281,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673aa3f60857e29ffa85d0645efab447848a0cc3","tid":1185281,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"呢到係少有綠色多的地方"},{"pid":"086b015190ca220193bc608687da9848f1bde8ce","tid":1185281,"uid":19126,"like":188,"dislike":6,"score":182,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"台灣班低智新物 講咩都會信<br />\n<br />\n邊個文盲錯字影衰哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706b5e8495fa3c1c7714d8e2d52482e2f336884a","tid":1185281,"uid":11148,"like":155,"dislike